\c 75
\s Rwiyo rwokuvonga Mwari
\d Kumutungamiriri wokuimba; nomuimbirwo weAritasheti. Pisarema raAsafi. Rwiyo.
\p
\v 1 Tinokuvongai, Mwari; Tinovonga, nokuti zita renyu riri pedyo; Vanhu vanoparidza mabasa enyu anoshamisa.
\v 2 "Kana ndichiwana nguva yakafanira, Ndichatonga zvakarurama.
\v 3 Pasi pose panyauka navose vagerepo; Ndini ndakamisa mbiru dzayo.
\v 4 Ndakati. huka Nax‘a. max‘yami, `Regai kuita namanyawi;' Nokuna vakaipa, `Regai kusimudza runyanga.'
\v 5 Regai kusimudza runyanga rwenyu kudenga; Regai kutaura nomutsipa mukukutu."
\v 6 Nokuti kunyange kumabudazuva, kana kumavirira, Kana kurenje, hakuzi ikoko kunobva kukudzwa.
\v 7 Asi Mwari ndiye mutongi; Anoninipisa mumwe achikudza mumwe.
\v 8 Nokuti muruoko rwaJehovha munomukombe, newaini inopupuma;
\s Uzere nezvakavhenganiswa, zvino anodurura mauri;
\s Zvirokwazvo, vakaipa vose venyika vachasvina masese awo, nokuanwa.
\p
\v 9 Asi ini ndichaparidza nokusingaperi,
\s Ndichaimbira Mwari waJakobho nziyo dzokurumbidza.
\p
\v 1 ° Nyanga dzose dzavakaipa ndichadzigura;
\s Asi nyanga dzavakarurama dzichasimudzwa.
